org.itsnat.comp.table

Interface ItsNatFreeTableHeader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatFreeComponent, ItsNatTableHeader, ItsNatUserData

    public interface ItsNatFreeTableHeader
extends ItsNatTableHeader, ItsNatFreeComponent
    Is the interface of the free table header components.

    ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface but is ever used (instanced) alongside a table component as the parent of this component.

    Author:
    Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
